    • newEnumDeserializer

      public static <T extends java.lang.Enum<T>> ArgumentDeserializer<T> newEnumDeserializer​(java.util.function.IntFunction<T[]> arrayGenerator)
      Creates a new ArgumentDeserializer that can deserialize Enums. Example: builder.addDeserializer(GameMode.class, Converters.newEnumDeserializer(GameMode[]::new));
      Type Parameters:
      T - the type of the enum
      Parameters:
      arrayGenerator - an array generator for the enum type
      Returns:
      the new deserializer
      See Also:
      CommandClientBuilder.addDeserializer(Class, ArgumentDeserializer)
